data.description: Discover tranquility in the hills of Tehachapi with this 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home at 22511 Zurich Dr. The interior features a spacious living area on both floors, and a cozy fireplace. The master suite includes a walk-in closet, and the property boasts scenic mountain views and an expansive deck for outdoor relaxation. This home offers a peaceful escape from city life.Nestled in a serene natural setting, this home provides the perfect retreat. Whether you're looking for a weekend getaway or a permanent residence, 22511 Zurich Dr offers the charm of mountain living in a convenient Tehachapi location.
